events.name: Boston Celtics at New York Knicks

headlines.description: — Jaylen Brown scored 30 points, Kristaps Porzingis had 22 and the NBA-leading Boston Celtics easily handled the New York Knicks 116-102 on Saturday night for their eighth consecutive victory.
headlines.shortLinkText: NBA-leading Celtics cruise to 8th straight win with 116-102 victory over Knicks
